OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMost will
OL,6,Fstay largely dry with the south seeing
OL,7,Fthe best of the late sunshine. However
OL,8,Fa few light showers cropping up around
OL,9,Fthe coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FSome patchy light rain
OL,12,Fpossible in the south and west, but
OL,13,Fmost staying dry and seeing spells of
OL,14,Fhazy sunshine. Winds light.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA dry
OL,17,Fstart to Monday with hazy sunshine.
OL,18,FHowever, occasional areas of rain
OL,19,Fcrossing the Province from the
OL,20,Fsouthwest from later Monday and
OL,21,Fthrough Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
